OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDIY waste charges ban could
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpush up council tax        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A ban on fees to get rid of DIY waste  
OL,6, in England will push up costs for all  
OL,7, households, councils have warned.      
OL,9,FBefore the ban, which came into force  
OL,10,Fon Sunday, around a third of local     
OL,11,Fauthorities charged to dispose of DIY  
OL,12,Fwaste at recycling centres.            
OL,14,FThe government said it wanted to deter 
OL,15,Ffly-tipping.                           
OL,17,FBut the Local Government Association   
OL,18,F(LGA) said the costs would still be    
OL,19,Fpassed on, for example through higher  
OL,20,Fcouncil tax.                           
